title: game of thrones
description: Emilia Clarke is an English actress best known for her role as Daenerys Targaryen in the HBO series Game of Thrones. She has received critical acclaim and several awards for her performance.

title: breaking bad
description: Anna Gunn is an American actress best known for her role as Skyler White in the critically acclaimed series Breaking Bad. Her performance earned her two Primetime Emmy Awards.

title: the crown
description: Claire Foy is an English actress who gained international fame for her portrayal of Queen Elizabeth II in the Netflix series The Crown, earning her several awards including a Golden Globe.

title: stranger things
description: Millie Bobby Brown is an English actress and producer, best known for her role as Eleven in the Netflix series Stranger Things, which has garnered her multiple award nominations.

title: the mandalorian
description: Gina Carano is an American actress and former mixed martial artist, known for her role as Cara Dune in the Disney+ series The Mandalorian, which has received widespread acclaim.

title: the handmaid's tale
description: Elisabeth Moss is an American actress and producer, widely recognized for her role as June Osborne in the Hulu series The Handmaid's Tale, earning her several Emmy nominations.
